<dashboard version="1.1" theme="dark">
  <label>Configure Trellix ePO Add-on</label>
  <description>Quick setup guide for Trellix (McAfee) ePO integration - Version 2.0.0</description>
  
  <row>
    <html>
      <style>
        .setup-container { 
          max-width: 900px; 
          margin: 0 auto; 
          padding: 20px;
          font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
        }
        .quick-start {
          background: linear-gradient(135deg, #238636 0%, #1f6feb 100%);
          border-radius: 16px;
          padding: 32px;
          margin-bottom: 24px;
          color: white;
          box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(35, 134, 54, 0.3);
        }
        .quick-start h1 {
          margin: 0 0 8px 0;
          font-size: 1.8em;
        }
        .quick-start p {
          margin: 0 0 20px 0;
          opacity: 0.9;
          font-size: 1.1em;
        }
        .quick-steps {
          display: flex;
          gap: 16px;
          flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .quick-step {
          background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
          border-radius: 12px;
          padding: 20px;
          flex: 1;
          min-width: 200px;
          backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }
        .quick-step .step-num {
          background: white;
          color: #238636;
          width: 32px;
          height: 32px;
          border-radius: 50%;
          display: inline-flex;
          align-items: center;
          justify-content: center;
          font-weight: bold;
          margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .quick-step h3 {
          margin: 0 0 8px 0;
          font-size: 1.1em;
        }
        .quick-step p {
          margin: 0;
          font-size: 0.9em;
          opacity: 0.85;
        }
        .setup-section {
          background: #21262d;
          border: 1px solid #30363d;
          border-radius: 12px;
          padding: 24px;
          margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .setup-section h2 {
          color: #58a6ff;
          margin-top: 0;
          padding-bottom: 12px;
          border-bottom: 1px solid #30363d;
          font-size: 1.3em;
        }
        .setup-section h3 {
          color: #c9d1d9;
          margin-top: 16px;
          font-size: 1.1em;
        }
        .info-box {
          background: #0d1117;
          border-left: 4px solid #238636;
          padding: 16px;
          margin: 16px 0;
          border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .warning-box {
          background: #0d1117;
          border-left: 4px solid #d29922;
          padding: 16px;
          margin: 16px 0;
          border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .success-box {
          background: #0d1117;
          border-left: 4px solid #3fb950;
          padding: 16px;
          margin: 16px 0;
          border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .code-block {
          background: #161b22;
          border: 1px solid #30363d;
          border-radius: 6px;
          padding: 12px 16px;
          font-family: 'SFMono-Regular', Consolas, monospace;
          font-size: 13px;
          overflow-x: auto;
          margin: 12px 0;
          color: #79c0ff;
          white-space: pre-wrap;
        }
        .btn-primary {
          background: #238636;
          color: white;
          border: none;
          padding: 12px 24px;
          border-radius: 8px;
          cursor: pointer;
          font-size: 14px;
          font-weight: 600;
          margin: 8px 8px 8px 0;
          text-decoration: none;
          display: inline-block;
          transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
          background: #2ea043;
          transform: translateY(-1px);
        }
        .btn-secondary {
          background: #21262d;
          color: #c9d1d9;
          border: 1px solid #30363d;
          padding: 12px 24px;
          border-radius: 8px;
          cursor: pointer;
          font-size: 14px;
          margin: 8px 8px 8px 0;
          text-decoration: none;
          display: inline-block;
          transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-secondary:hover {
          border-color: #58a6ff;
          color: #58a6ff;
        }
        .config-table {
          width: 100%;
          border-collapse: collapse;
          margin: 16px 0;
        }
        .config-table th, .config-table td {
          padding: 12px;
          text-align: left;
          border-bottom: 1px solid #30363d;
        }
        .config-table th {
          background: #161b22;
          color: #58a6ff;
          font-weight: 600;
        }
        .config-table tr:hover {
          background: rgba(56, 139, 253, 0.1);
        }
        .priority-high { color: #f85149; font-weight: 600; }
        .priority-medium { color: #d29922; }
        .priority-low { color: #8b949e; }
        .copy-btn {
          background: #30363d;
          color: #c9d1d9;
          border: none;
          padding: 4px 12px;
          border-radius: 4px;
          cursor: pointer;
          font-size: 12px;
          float: right;
        }
        .copy-btn:hover {
          background: #484f58;
        }
        .tab-container {
          display: flex;
          border-bottom: 1px solid #30363d;
          margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .tab {
          padding: 12px 20px;
          cursor: pointer;
          color: #8b949e;
          border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
          margin-bottom: -1px;
        }
        .tab.active {
          color: #58a6ff;
          border-bottom-color: #58a6ff;
        }
        .tab:hover {
          color: #c9d1d9;
        }
      </style>
      
      <div class="setup-container">
        
        <!-- Quick Start Hero Section -->
        <div class="quick-start">
          <h1>🚀 Quick Start Guide</h1>
          <p>Get your Trellix ePO integration running in 3 simple steps</p>
          
          <div class="quick-steps">
            <div class="quick-step">
              <div class="step-num">1</div>
              <h3>Configure Server</h3>
              <p>Set your ePO server URL, port, and username in the settings file</p>
            </div>
            <div class="quick-step">
              <div class="step-num">2</div>
              <h3>Store Password</h3>
              <p>Securely store your ePO password using the credential script</p>
            </div>
            <div class="quick-step">
              <div class="step-num">3</div>
              <h3>Enable Inputs</h3>
              <p>Choose which data sources to collect and restart Splunk</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Step 1: Server Configuration -->
        <div class="setup-section">
          <h2>📋 Step 1: Configure ePO Server Settings</h2>
          
          <div class="info-box">
            <strong>💡 Quick Tip:</strong> You only need to set <code>epo_server</code> and <code>username</code>. All other settings have sensible defaults.
          </div>
          
          <h3>Create Your Configuration File</h3>
          <div class="code-block">
# Linux/macOS
cp $SPLUNK_HOME/etc/apps/TA-trellix-epo/default/ta_trellix_epo_settings.conf \
   $SPLUNK_HOME/etc/apps/TA-trellix-epo/local/ta_trellix_epo_settings.conf

# Windows (PowerShell)
Copy-Item "$env:SPLUNK_HOME\etc\apps\TA-trellix-epo\default\ta_trellix_epo_settings.conf" `
          "$env:SPLUNK_HOME\etc\apps\TA-trellix-epo\local\ta_trellix_epo_settings.conf"
          </div>
          
          <h3>Edit the Configuration (Minimum Required)</h3>
          <div class="code-block">
[general]
epo_server = your-epo-server.company.com
username = your_epo_username
          </div>
          
          <details>
            <summary style="cursor: pointer; color: #58a6ff; margin: 16px 0;"><strong>▶ View All Configuration Options</strong></summary>
            <table class="config-table">
              <tr><th>Setting</th><th>Description</th><th>Default</th><th>Required</th></tr>
              <tr><td><code>epo_server</code></td><td>ePO server hostname or IP</td><td>—</td><td>✅ Yes</td></tr>
              <tr><td><code>username</code></td><td>ePO API username</td><td>—</td><td>✅ Yes</td></tr>
              <tr><td><code>epo_port</code></td><td>ePO server port</td><td>8443</td><td>No</td></tr>
              <tr><td><code>use_ssl</code></td><td>Use HTTPS connection</td><td>true</td><td>No</td></tr>
              <tr><td><code>verify_ssl</code></td><td>Verify SSL certificate</td><td>true</td><td>No</td></tr>
              <tr><td><code>timeout</code></td><td>Request timeout (seconds)</td><td>60</td><td>No</td></tr>
              <tr><td><code>batch_size</code></td><td>Events per API call</td><td>1000</td><td>No</td></tr>
              <tr><td><code>log_level</code></td><td>DEBUG, INFO, WARNING, ERROR</td><td>INFO</td><td>No</td></tr>
            </table>
          </details>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Step 2: Password Configuration -->
        <div class="setup-section">
          <h2>🔐 Step 2: Store Password Securely</h2>
          
          <div class="warning-box">
            <strong>⚠️ Security:</strong> Never store passwords in plain text files. Use one of the methods below.
          </div>
          
          <h3>Option A: Interactive Script (Recommended)</h3>
          <div class="code-block">
# Linux/macOS
sudo $SPLUNK_HOME/bin/splunk cmd python $SPLUNK_HOME/etc/apps/TA-trellix-epo/bin/configure_credentials.py

# Windows (Run as Administrator)
%SPLUNK_HOME%\bin\splunk cmd python %SPLUNK_HOME%\etc\apps\TA-trellix-epo\bin\configure_credentials.py
          </div>
          <p style="color: #8b949e; font-size: 0.9em;">The script will prompt for Splunk admin credentials, then your ePO username and password.</p>
          
          <h3>Option B: Direct curl Command</h3>
          <div class="code-block">
curl -k -u admin:SPLUNK_PASSWORD \
  https://localhost:8089/servicesNS/nobody/TA-trellix-epo/storage/passwords \
  -d name=YOUR_EPO_USERNAME \
  -d password="YOUR_EPO_PASSWORD" \
  -d realm=TA-trellix-epo
          </div>
          
          <div class="success-box">
            <strong>✅ Success:</strong> You should see "Created credential" or "Updated credential" message.
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Step 3: Enable Inputs -->
        <div class="setup-section">
          <h2>📥 Step 3: Enable Data Inputs</h2>
          
          <h3>Create Your Inputs Configuration</h3>
          <div class="code-block">
# Linux/macOS
cp $SPLUNK_HOME/etc/apps/TA-trellix-epo/default/inputs.conf \
   $SPLUNK_HOME/etc/apps/TA-trellix-epo/local/inputs.conf

# Windows (PowerShell)
Copy-Item "$env:SPLUNK_HOME\etc\apps\TA-trellix-epo\default\inputs.conf" `
          "$env:SPLUNK_HOME\etc\apps\TA-trellix-epo\local\inputs.conf"
          </div>
          
          <h3>Enable the Inputs You Need</h3>
          <p>Edit <code>local/inputs.conf</code> and change <code>disabled = 1</code> to <code>disabled = 0</code>:</p>
          
          <table class="config-table">
            <tr><th>Input</th><th>Description</th><th>Priority</th><th>Interval</th></tr>
            <tr><td><code>threat_events</code></td><td>Security threats and detections</td><td class="priority-high">HIGH</td><td>5 min</td></tr>
            <tr><td><code>malware_detections</code></td><td>Malware identification</td><td class="priority-high">HIGH</td><td>5 min</td></tr>
            <tr><td><code>quarantine_events</code></td><td>Quarantine actions</td><td class="priority-high">HIGH</td><td>10 min</td></tr>
            <tr><td><code>host_status</code></td><td>Endpoint inventory</td><td class="priority-medium">MEDIUM</td><td>1 hour</td></tr>
            <tr><td><code>agent_status</code></td><td>Agent connectivity</td><td class="priority-medium">MEDIUM</td><td>1 hour</td></tr>
            <tr><td><code>policy_compliance</code></td><td>Compliance monitoring</td><td class="priority-medium">MEDIUM</td><td>2 hours</td></tr>
            <tr><td><code>user_actions</code></td><td>Admin audit logs</td><td class="priority-medium">MEDIUM</td><td>10 min</td></tr>
            <tr><td><code>updates</code></td><td>DAT version tracking</td><td class="priority-low">LOW</td><td>4 hours</td></tr>
          </table>
          
          <h3>Example: Enable Threat Monitoring</h3>
          <div class="code-block">
[trellix_epo://threat_events]
disabled = 0
interval = 300
index = main

[trellix_epo://malware_detections]
disabled = 0
interval = 300
index = main
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Step 4: Restart and Verify -->
        <div class="setup-section">
          <h2>🔄 Step 4: Restart Splunk and Verify</h2>
          
          <h3>Restart Splunk</h3>
          <div class="code-block">
# Linux/macOS
$SPLUNK_HOME/bin/splunk restart

# Windows
%SPLUNK_HOME%\bin\splunk restart
          </div>
          
          <h3>Verify Data is Flowing</h3>
          <div class="code-block">
index=main sourcetype="trellix_epo:*" | head 10
          </div>
          
          <div class="success-box">
            <strong>🎉 All Done!</strong> Your Trellix ePO integration is now active. Visit the Security Command Center to view your data.
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Quick Links -->
        <div class="setup-section">
          <h2>🔗 Quick Actions</h2>
          <p>
            <a href="/app/TA-trellix-epo/trellix_epo_overview" class="btn-primary">📊 View Dashboard</a>
            <a href="/manager/TA-trellix-epo/data/inputs/trellix_epo" class="btn-primary">⚙️ Manage Inputs</a>
            <a href="/app/TA-trellix-epo/search?q=index%3D*%20sourcetype%3D%22trellix_epo%3A*%22%20%7C%20head%2050" class="btn-secondary">🔍 Search Data</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/sarat1kyan/TA-trellix-epo" target="_blank" class="btn-secondary">📖 Documentation</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/sarat1kyan/TA-trellix-epo/issues" target="_blank" class="btn-secondary">🐛 Report Issue</a>
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Troubleshooting -->
        <div class="setup-section">
          <h2>🔧 Troubleshooting</h2>
          
          <details>
            <summary style="cursor: pointer; color: #58a6ff; margin: 8px 0;"><strong>▶ No data appearing?</strong></summary>
            <div style="padding: 12px 0;">
              <ol>
                <li>Check that inputs are enabled (<code>disabled = 0</code>)</li>
                <li>Verify ePO server is reachable: <code>curl -k https://your-epo-server:8443</code></li>
                <li>Check Splunk logs: <code>index=_internal sourcetype=splunkd component=ModularInputs trellix</code></li>
                <li>Verify credentials are stored: <code>| rest /servicesNS/nobody/TA-trellix-epo/storage/passwords</code></li>
              </ol>
            </div>
          </details>
          
          <details>
            <summary style="cursor: pointer; color: #58a6ff; margin: 8px 0;"><strong>▶ SSL Certificate errors?</strong></summary>
            <div style="padding: 12px 0;">
              <p>If your ePO server uses a self-signed certificate, set in <code>local/ta_trellix_epo_settings.conf</code>:</p>
              <div class="code-block">verify_ssl = false</div>
              <p style="color: #d29922;">⚠️ Only use this in development/testing environments.</p>
            </div>
          </details>
          
          <details>
            <summary style="cursor: pointer; color: #58a6ff; margin: 8px 0;"><strong>▶ Authentication failures?</strong></summary>
            <div style="padding: 12px 0;">
              <ol>
                <li>Verify the ePO username has API access permissions</li>
                <li>Check password is correctly stored (re-run configure_credentials.py)</li>
                <li>Ensure username in settings matches the stored credential</li>
              </ol>
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #8b949e; font-size: 12px;">
          <p>Trellix ePO Add-on v2.0.0 | <a href="https://splunkbase.splunk.com/app/8351" target="_blank" style="color: #58a6ff;">Splunkbase</a> | <a href="https://github.com/sarat1kyan/TA-trellix-epo" target="_blank" style="color: #58a6ff;">GitHub</a></p>
        </div>
        
      </div>
    </html>
  </row>
</dashboard>
